# Upload-Post Social Media Connection Guide

## Overview
This document explains how to connect your social media accounts to Upload-Post (https://www.upload-post.com/) for automated video posting across multiple platforms.

---

## Prerequisites

Before you begin, ensure you have:
- ✅ Active accounts on the social media platforms you want to connect
- ✅ **A Facebook Business Page** (required for Facebook connections)
- ✅ Browser access with all social media accounts logged in
- ✅ Upload-Post account (Note: TikTok connection requires a paid subscription)

---

## Step-by-Step Connection Process

### 1. Access Upload-Post
- Navigate to https://www.upload-post.com/
- Log in to your Upload-Post account
- Go to your **User Settings** or **Connected Accounts** section

### 2. Connect Each Social Media Platform

You will need to approve each social media connection individually. Follow these steps for each platform:

#### **YouTube**
1. Click on the YouTube connection option
2. You will be redirected to Google login/authorization
3. Select the Google account associated with your YouTube channel
4. Click **Allow** to grant Upload-Post permission to post on your behalf
5. You will be redirected back to Upload-Post upon successful connection

#### **Facebook**
1. Click on the Facebook connection option
2. Log in to Facebook if prompted
3. **Important:** Select your **Facebook Business Page** (not your personal profile)
4. Review the permissions requested
5. Click **Confirm** or **Allow** to authorize the connection
6. Verify that your Business Page name appears as connected

#### **Instagram**
1. Click on the Instagram connection option
2. Log in to your Instagram account if prompted
3. Review the permissions requested
4. Click **Authorize** to grant access
5. Confirm the connection was successful

#### **TikTok** *(Paid Users Only)*
1. Click on the TikTok connection option
2. Log in to your TikTok account if prompted
3. Review the permissions requested
4. Click **Authorize** to grant access
5. Confirm the connection was successful

---

## Verification

After connecting each platform:
1. Return to your Upload-Post dashboard
2. Verify that all connected accounts show a **"Connected"** or **green checkmark** status
3. Test by posting a sample video to ensure everything works correctly

---

## Important Notes

⚠️ **Facebook Requirement:** You must have a Facebook Business Page. Personal profiles cannot be used for automated posting.

⚠️ **TikTok Limitation:** TikTok connection is only available for paid Upload-Post subscribers.

✅ **Tested Platforms:** YouTube, Facebook, and Instagram connections have been successfully tested and verified.

---
